package.Name: ** Ex Mumbai ** Thailand Fixed Departure (2N Pattaya + 2N Bangkok)

Standard.hotel: Galleria 12 Bangkok Hotel by Compass Hospitality

rows.Inclusion:
• Direct Flight from Mumbai to Bangkok
  • Return Airport Transfers in Thailand on SIC
  • 4 Nights Accommodation in above mentioned hotel or Similar
  • 4 Breakfast included in the cost
  • Intercity Transfers (Bangkok to Pattaya and return) on SIC basis
  • Visit to Coral Island by speed boat and with lunch in Pattaya on SIC
  • Bangkok city orientation tour which includes the Golden Buddha and Marble Buddha on SIC
  • GST
rows.Exclusions:
• Visa is not included in above cost
  • Thai Pass is not included in above mentioned cost
  • TCS will be applicable as per Govt. regulations
  • Guide is not included in above package.
  • All personal expenses like tips, laundry, telephone calls/fax, alcoholic beverages, camera/video camera fees at monuments, entrances fees, medical expenses, airport departure tax etc.
  • Anything, which is not mentioned under Package Inclusions.
  • Cost incidental to any change in the itinerary/stay on an account of flight cancellation due to bad weather, ill health, and roadblocks and/or any factors beyond control.
  • For any unutilized service no refund will be provided
  • Any Kind of Travel or Health Insurance is not included in mentioned cost.
